headline: Is Elevance Health (ELV) Pricing Lagging Its Strong Cash Flow Valuation Models
summary: If you are wondering whether Elevance Health's current share price actually reflects its underlying worth, you are not alone. That is exactly what this article is here to unpack. The stock recently closed at US$372.83, with returns of 5.2% over the last week, 9.3% over the last month, 5.2% year to date, and a small 0.3% decline over the past year.
